# Build artifacts — never committed. `dist/` is trunk's wasm bundle output;
# `target/` is this standalone crate's build dir. Cargo.lock IS committed
# (unlike the run-by-hand dev/* spikes) so the exact transitive dependency set
# proven to build on Rust 1.95 stays reproducible for later UI tasks and for
# the rust-embed step that bakes dist/ into paavo-web.
/target
/dist
